info.description:
Plugin/extension library for Circuits and Circuits.Web

Requires:
	Circuits 2.1
	
Optional:
	BSON
	BeautifulSoup4
	Mako
	
While this library may be installed via PyPi it is recommended to clone the
repository located at http://bitbucket.org/jgiorgi/frankencircuits. The
reposity contains addition resources such as drop-in implementations and
examples.

Beginner documentation and tutorials are available at
http://bitbucket.org/jgiorgi/frankencircuits/wiki. Full API documentation is
available as python docstrings. The code is also well commented and extensible.

Feel free to submit any comments, concerns or requests via the issue tracker
on bitbucket or via email justin@justingiorgi.com.
